        <cdata>
          <text>&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;504 Loan Availability Act&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;This bill temporarily combines the funding authorization for loans and refinancing loans under the Small Business Administration 504 loan program. The 504 loan program provides financing for major fixed assets through community-based Certified Development Companies (CDCs).&lt;/p&gt;</text>
        </cdata>
      </summary>
